Murphy is a sailor who is located at Port Khazard. To reach him quickly, use the Minigame teleport to Fishing Trawler. Players must speak to him in the Recipe for Disaster sub-quest, Pirate Pete, in order to obtain a diving apparatus to go diving. He runs the Fishing Trawler minigame and also gives players a sextant which is 1 of 3 items that the observatory professor tells you is needed to solve a coordinate in a Treasure Trail.
